<h2 class="contentheading">
	A Flash-based mp3 player</h2>



<p class="buttonheading">
	</p>






I've integrated an mp3 player originally written by Jeroen Wijering ( <a href="http://www.jeroenwijering.com/">http://www.jeroenwijering.com/</a> ) into a Joomla component. <a href="/mp3player.zip">Click here to downoload it</a>. You can use the backend to customize your own playlist as well as adjust a few of the parameters. This development has been in conjunction with a larger project commissioned by Siobhan Ramsey: <a href="http://www.sandboxeducation.co.uk/">http://www.sandboxeducation.co.uk/</a>.

